---
title: Tandoori Style Chicken on Golden Naan with a sweetcorn and chilli salsa
description: The preparation of tandoori chicken involves it being marinated in spiced yoghurt then roasted in an oven known as a tandoor, hence the dish's name. Though this dish may not utilize a clay oven, the deep flavour bestowed by the marinade is definitely there.
